Basic requirement is to install node.
>in terminal

1.npm init 
-to install package.json

2.npm install -D tailwindcss
-it will install tainwindcss in as dev dependancy.
-node_modules and package-lock.json files install

3.npx tailwindcss init
-it will install tainwind.config.js file

4.>open tailwind.config.js file 
 --> update
  content: ['./index.html']

5.> open style.css and add
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

6.in terminal generate output.css file as tailindcss
>npx tailwindcss -i ./style.css -o ./output.css --watch

7.Now link output.css with index.html file